maintenance_action: Description: PT_CSH11 failed to swing to reverse during point testing in the greenfield. All points were operated individually, not via a route setting. TC1 locked PT_CSH11 in normal. PT_CSH12, CSH21 and PT_CSH22 all operational. MSS shows PT_CSH11 as available with no errors.; Root Cause: A power loss, the power needed is 110 volts he has measured 50 volts and the motor stalls before the completing the movement. Spare power cable core to parallel up the power supply to remove the voltage drop issue.
